<h2 id="dumping-the-upcoming-invoice">Dumping the Upcoming Invoice <a class="headerlink" href="calculate-upgrade-cost#dumping-the-upcoming-invoice" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
